This flag triggers the autopilot worker to disable scheduled workflows
in all sister repositories (ecosystem2, ecosystem3, ecosystem-5, 
new-ecosysstem, new2, tiny-new).

The worker should:
1. Read the task file: .autopilot/tasks/disable-sister-repo-workflows.json
2. Execute the steps defined in the task
3. Generate a report: SISTER_REPOS_DISABLED_REPORT.md
4. Remove this flag file when complete

Expected completion time: 15-20 minutes
